<br />
<br />EDIT: I have started to develop the image archiving tool. I'll test it first on GB/SNES/Other Retro, and I'll run it from home so as not to burden Parodius with extra Internet bandwidth. Some images will not be archived because the server disallows robots or forbids Referer: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://nesdev.com/bbs/">http://nesdev.com/bbs/</a><!-- m --> .

		

