		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Four steps:
<br /><ol style="list-style-type: decimal"><li>Install <a href="http://code.google.com/p/html5lib/" class="postlink">html5lib</a> </li><li>Download <a href="http://pineight.com/pc/scrape_privmsg.py.zip" class="postlink">the archiver</a> and unzip it </li><li>Edit the username and password </li><li>From a terminal window, <strong>python scrape_privmsg.py</strong> </li></ol>

		

